Package optimization.stochastic.operators.onFloats

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AffineFloatRecombiner
    Class that performs affine recombination of float features.
    BlendFloatRecombiner
    Class that performs blend recombination of feature values.
    HeterogenousFloatMutator
    Heterogenous float mutator, mutating float features in such a way that different features have different mutations rates.
    HeterogenousTwoDevsFloatMutator
    Heterogenous float mutator where each feature has a separate probability of mutating by a small or a large amount.
    HomogenousFloatMutator
    Homogenous float mutator that mutates the values of float features in data points.
    HomogenousTwoDevsFloatMutator
    A class that implements the homogenous two deviations float mutator.
    PointSetTwoDevMutation
    Mutation class for point set configurations.
    SwapFloatRecombiner
    A recombination method where parts of two genotypes are randomly swapped by a certain probability.
